form where the underground music has its own place to thrive.</p></div></div></div></div></div></header></div></div></section>\n<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-e72f9fe elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"e72f9fe\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"animation\":\"none\",\"animation_delay\":15}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-55d8303 elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"55d8303\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\"animation\":\"fadeIn\",\"animation_delay\":10,\"background_background\":\"classic\"}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap lazyelementorbackgroundimages elementor-element-populated\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efc032a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"efc032a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-image\"> <img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"./Broken Radio - Where Electronic Music has a place to thrive!_files/music-box-1419792_1920-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"what kind of music you can listen on broken radio\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"//d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920-1024x683.jpg 1024w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920-300x200.jpg 300w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920-768x512.jpg 768w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920-1200x800.jpg 1200w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/music-box-1419792_1920.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" class=\"attachment-large size-large no-lazyload\"></div></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb2ec07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bb2ec07\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What is Electronic Music?</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0159fa7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0159fa7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Electronic music has a wide spectrum of genres.</p><p>From very bouncy and mainly dancefloor worthy like Techno, Drum and Bass, House, Trance (to name a few) to sounds you enjoy predominately at home like ambient, new wave, chill out, trip hop.</p><p>Broken Radio will try to meet any expectations. Want to know more? Click <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_electronic_music_genres\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">>HERE<</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-87fb5e8 elementor-invisible\" data-id=\"87fb5e8\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\"animation\":\"fadeIn\",\"animation_delay\":10,\"background_background\":\"classic\"}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap lazyelementorbackgroundimages elementor-element-populated\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-734f5d9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"734f5d9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How can you listen to us</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed34159 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ed34159\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\"><p>Firstly, You can listen to Broken Radio on any device connected to the interwebz! However, for best experience, use modern browsers/devices.</p> <p>Secondly, if you do want to view live video Dj streams, use unlimited data connection, Broken Radio should be free, keep it that way!</p></div></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-54ae3f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"54ae3f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-image\"> <img onload=\"Wpfcll.r(this,true);\" src=\"./Broken Radio - Where Electronic Music has a place to thrive!_files/blank.gif\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" data-wpfc-original-src=\"//d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"what devices can be used to connect to broken radio\" loading=\"lazy\" data-wpfc-original-srcset=\"//d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-1024x683.jpg 1024w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-300x200.jpg 300w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-768x512.jpg 768w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920-1200x800.jpg 1200w, //d4c2v3v2.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/plug-1859843_1920.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" class=\"attachment-large size-large no-lazyload\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=