ell free to abuse the connection!</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section>\n<footer class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-52bc11b elementor-section-content-middle elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"52bc11b\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{\"background_background\":\"classic\"}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7a57106e\" data-id=\"7a57106e\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{\"background_background\":\"classic\"}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap lazyelementorbackgroundimages elementor-element-populated\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a678b6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4a678b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Social Links:</h2></div></div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-30299a3d elementor-shape-circle elementor-grid-0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-social-icons\" data-id=\"30299a3d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"social-icons.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-social-icons-wrapper elementor-grid\">\n<div class=\"elementor-grid-item\"> <a class=\"elementor-icon elementor-social-icon elementor-social-icon-facebook-f elementor-repeater-item-4cd9d92\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/brokendotradio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <span class=\"elementor-screen-only\">Facebook-f</span> <i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i> </a></div><div class=\"elementor-grid-item\"> <a class=\"elementor-icon elementor-social-icon elementor-